password     requisite     pam_cracklib.so try_first_pass difok=8 retry=3 minlen=14 minclass=4 maxrepeat=2 maxclassrepeat=2 maxsequence=4 dcredit=-1 ucredit=-1 lcredit=-1 ocredit=-1 gecoscheck reject_username enforce_for_root
password     sufficient    pam_unix.so sha512 rounds=10000 shadow try_first_pass use_authtok remember=5
password     sufficient    pam_ldap.so use_authtok ignore_unknown_user ignore_authinfo_unavail
password     required      pam_deny.so

